text: Origin of Symmetry is the second album by Muse. Muse is an English rock band. The band released the album on 18 July 2001. The British Phonographic Industry (BPI) gave the album a platinum certification. It was number three on the UK Albums Chart. The album had four singles. These are "Plug In Baby", "New Born", "Bliss", and "Hyper Music" / "Feeling Good". ==Songs== #New Born #Bliss #Space Dementia #Hyper Music #Plug In Baby #Citizen Erased #Micro Cuts #Feeling Good #Screenager #Dark Shines #Megalomania #Futurism ==References== Category:2001 albums Category:Muse albums
